# color object foregr backg option
#---------------------------------

# GENERAL config
## error message. Cursor line. Status bar. Tilde.
    color error color1 color236
    color indicator default color238
    color status color4 color236
    color tilde	default default

# INDEX config
## Default colors
    color index default  default '.*'
## New messages. Replied messages. Deleted messages. Messages in a thread.
    color index color2 default ~N
    color index color4 default ~Q
    color index	color1 default ~D
    color index	color4 default ~v

# PAGER config 
## Header Colors
### default header colors
    color hdrdefault color2 color236
### subject color. Attachment color
    color header color5 color236 ^Subject:.*
    color attachment color4 color236
## Body Colors
### Mail addresses. Urls. Quotation. Signature.
    color body color4	default [\-\.+_a-zA-Z0-9]+@[\-\.a-zA-Z0-9]+
    color body color4	default	(https?|ftp)://[\-\.,/%~_:?&=\#a-zA-Z0-9]+
    color quoted color1 default
## Footer Colors
### signature color
    color signature  color5 default

